qryXMLSLATIDetail.Description:
Snuff: 19 cents per each 1.5 ounces or portion thereof by net weight sold;
Chewing Tobacco: 19 cents per each single unit (contain 4 oz. or less by net weight), 40 cents per each half pound unit (contains 4 to 8 oz. by net weight) and 65 cents per each pound unit (contains 8 to 16 oz. by net weight) sold;
Other tobacco products: 15% of the actual price for which the distributor sells tobacco products, except snuff and chewing tobacco, within Kentucky.

Cigarette Wholesalers: $500 per year;
Tobacco Product Distributors: $500 per year (no charge if they have cigarette wholesale license already); 
Vending Machine Operators: $25 per year.
